DESCRIPTION: Add, remove, copy, and download emojis from other servers to your server.
EXAMPLE:
{{prefix}}emoji add <:SkyeZumbi:823046656387055646> **- to add the emoji to the server**
{{prefix}}emoji remove <:SkyeZumbi:823046656387055646> **- to remove the emoji from the server**
{{prefix}}emoji list** - to see the list of emojis on the server**
{{prefix}}emoji download <:SkyeZumbi:823046656387055646> ** - to get the download link for the emoji**
